{"id":60118,"type":6,"name":"Harry Potter and the Prisoner of Azkaban","name_cn":"哈利·波特与阿兹卡班囚徒","date":"2004-06-04","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/6b/9f/60118_l0VCQ.jpg","rating":{"rank":727,"total":289,"count":{"1":0,"2":0,"3":0,"4":2,"5":8,"6":25,"7":95,"8":120,"9":26,"10":13},"score":7.6},"summary":"哈利（丹尼尔·雷德克里夫）即将在霍格沃兹渡过第三个年头，此时在阿兹塔班却传出恶棍小天狼星（加里·奥德曼）越狱的消息。据说小天狼星正是背叛哈利父母的好友，他的教父，而这次小天狼星越狱似乎正是为了找他。哈利的心里悄悄的滋生了为父母报仇的想法，期待着小天狼星的出现。\r\n　　新来的魔法老师卢平（大卫·休里斯）有着桀骜不驯的个性，与哈利关系很好，教了哈利许多实用的黑魔法防御知识。而此时在他的魔法地图上却出现了一个神秘人物，虫尾巴。偶然的机会下，在尖叫棚屋里集齐了哈利父亲当年的所有好友，卢平、虫尾巴、小天狼星，哈利的魔杖直指向小天狼星，但他发现那罪犯看他的眼神里充满了疼爱…… ","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>哈利·波特与阿兹卡班囚徒</li><li><span>原作: </span><a href=\"/person/25410\">J. K. Rowling</a></li><li><span>音乐: </span><a href=\"/person/13969\">John Williams</a></li><li><span>主演: </span><a href=\"/person/40303\">Harry Melling</a>、<a href=\"/person/40291\">Fiona Shaw</a>、<a href=\"/person/40261\">Robbie Coltrane</a>、<a href=\"/person/40304\">Richard Griffiths</a>、<a href=\"/person/40309\">Julie Walters</a>、<a href=\"/person/40330\">Matthew Lewis</a>、<a href=\"/person/39694\">Bonnie Wright</a>、<a href=\"/person/40305\">Warwick Davis</a>、<a href=\"/person/39688\">Tom Felton</a>、<a href=\"/person/39638\">Daniel Radcliffe</a>、<a href=\"/person/33504\">Gary Oldman</a>、<a href=\"/person/39646\">Rupert Grint</a>、<a href=\"/person/39647\">Alan Rickman</a>、<a href=\"/person/39649\">Maggie Smith</a>、<a href=\"/person/39648\">Michael Gambon</a>、<a href=\"/person/23742\">Emma Watson</a></li><li><span>制作: </span><a href=\"/person/26177\">Industrial Light and Magic</a></li><li><span>别名: </span>哈利·波特与阿兹卡班的囚徒</li><li><span>集数: </span>1</li><li><span>开始: </span>2004-06-04</li><li><span>类型: </span>悬疑 / 家庭 / 奇幻 / 冒险</li><li><span>国家/地区: </span>英国 / 美国</li><li><span>语言: </span>英语</li><li><span>每集长: </span>141 分钟</li><li><span>imdb_id: </span>0304141</li><li><span>导演: </span>Alfonso Cuarón</li>","collection":{"on_hold":0,"dropped":2,"wish":6,"collect":493,"doing":2},"tags":[{"name"